full_text: OPTAPHI will train 14 #PhD researchers in #optical #sensing combining #photoacoustic and #photothermal #spectroscopy with #laser design and fabrication. Partners include @CIT_ie @PolibaOfficial @unibait @tuvienna and @umontpellier in Ireland, Italy, Austria & France. @cappa_cit
